I often make edits to a confluence page or blog post in response to comments that have been added.  Since Confluence doesn't show the comments while you are editing a page, I have to edit the page in a different tab/window than the one I'm viewing it in.  This is a PITA, plus it sometimes results in conflicting changes if I leave the computer, come back and start editing the page in multiple windows.

This simple improvement would result in a big productivity boost for a lot of users.

